de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.datasource.filter

Class NaNFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.datasource.filter.AbstractStreamFilter
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.datasource.filter.NaNFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BundleStreamSource, ObjectFilter, StreamFilter

    public class NaNFilter
extends AbstractStreamFilter
    A filter to drop all records that contain NaN values. Note: currently, only dense vector columns are supported. TODO: add support for sparse vectors.
